changeList.Description: Added the [findRooms](/graph/api/user-findRooms?view=graph-rest-beta) method to the [user](/graph/api/resources/user?view=graph-rest-beta) resource
Changed the type of the **year** property in the [standardTimeZoneOffset](/graph/api/resources/standardTimeZoneOffset?view=graph-rest-beta) resource
Changed the type of the **isSubscribedByMail** property in the [group](/graph/api/resources/group?view=graph-rest-beta) resource
Changed the **isSubscribedByMail** property in the [group](/graph/api/resources/group?view=graph-rest-beta) resource from optional to required
Removed the `saturday` member from the **dayOfWeek** enumeration
Removed the **EmailAddresses** parameter from the [getMailTips](/graph/api/user-getMailTips?view=graph-rest-beta) method
Changed the **StartDateTime** parameter in the [reminderView](/graph/api/user-reminderView?view=graph-rest-beta) method from required to optional
Removed the **findRooms** method from the [user](/graph/api/resources/user?view=graph-rest-beta) resource
